  "body": " Unit Conversions  Mass in one unit can easily converted to other units by using simple conversion factors. Some important mass relations to remember are:    Mass Conversion 1   Convert 2 metric tons to pounds.               Mass Conversion 2   Convert 600 oz to kg.              "
